<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 12:12:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴勒斯坦卫生部：约旦河西岸与以色列军队交火造成四人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-four-dead-in-fire-exchange-with-israeli-army-in-west-bank/0000018c-7c84-d98c-abef-fe9783d50000</link><description>以色列军队称，士兵们在法拉难民营连夜行动，逮捕了一名通缉犯，并没收了一支步枪。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 12:04:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-four-dead-in-fire-exchange-with-israeli-army-in-west-bank/0000018c-7c84-d98c-abef-fe9783d50000</guid></item><item><title>“我们正在打造大屠杀纪念馆 2.0”：与时间赛跑，记录 10 月 7 日大屠杀的恐怖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-race-against-time-to-document-the-horrors-of-the-october-7-massacre-in-southern-israel/0000018c-77be-d250-a1af-ffbf61640000</link><description>一项庞大的项目正在进行中，以扫描和记录每个被烧毁的房间和扭断的窗框、每个弹孔和烧焦的椅子、每个破损的洋娃娃和废弃的仙人掌花园。就在他们于 10 月 7 日离开时，也就是哈马斯袭击以色列边境社区的那一天</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 12:02:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-race-against-time-to-document-the-horrors-of-the-october-7-massacre-in-southern-israel/0000018c-77be-d250-a1af-ffbf61640000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女在约旦河西岸枪击事件中受轻伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-woman-wounded-in-west-bank-shooting-attack/0000018c-7c44-d55c-a7cc-ff469c500000</link><description>以色列国防军估计枪击事件是从一辆路过的车辆上进行的。这是过去两个月内在约旦河西岸发生的第三起针对以色列人的枪击事件</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 11:10:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-woman-wounded-in-west-bank-shooting-attack/0000018c-7c44-d55c-a7cc-ff469c500000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙杀害了数千名儿童。这么多以色列人怎么能漠不关心呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-killed-thousands-of-children-in-gaza-how-can-so-many-israelis-remain-indifferent/0000018c-788c-d55c-a7cc-fb8edb100000</link><description>几十年来，我们从小就相信只有军事力量才能确保国家的生存，同时又剥夺巴勒斯坦人的权利。这只是这个问题的众多悲伤答案之一</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 11:09:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-killed-thousands-of-children-in-gaza-how-can-so-many-israelis-remain-indifferent/0000018c-788c-d55c-a7cc-fb8edb100000</guid></item><item><title>阵亡的以色列士兵是德国人的孙子，他们来到以色列为大屠杀赎罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/fallen-idf-soldier-was-grandson-of-germans-who-came-to-israel-to-atone-for-holocaust/0000018c-7c40-d98c-abef-fed78bdc0000</link><description>来自 Ma&amp;#39;alot-Tarshiha 的 20 岁以色列士兵 Urija Bayer 的祖父母于 1984 年在以色列北部为大屠杀幸存者建立了疗养院</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 10:38:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/fallen-idf-soldier-was-grandson-of-germans-who-came-to-israel-to-atone-for-holocaust/0000018c-7c40-d98c-abef-fed78bdc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列地方议会主席在电台采访中呼吁“像今天的奥斯威辛一样夷平加沙”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/israeli-local-council-head-calls-to-flatten-gaza-like-auschwitz-today-in-radio-interview/0000018c-7bf9-de44-a9be-7ffd05e90000</link><description>以色列北部地方议会主席呼吁将加沙人“装载”到以色列海军舰艇上并带到黎巴嫩难民营，将加沙变成博物馆，“这样全世界都会了解以色列可以做什么”</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 09:58:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/israeli-local-council-head-calls-to-flatten-gaza-like-auschwitz-today-in-radio-interview/0000018c-7bf9-de44-a9be-7ffd05e90000</guid></item><item><title>“哈佛没有太多反犹太主义”：犹太诺贝尔奖获得者为哈佛校长辩护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jewish-nobel-prize-laureate-explains-his-support-for-harvard-head/0000018c-7888-d7be-a1cd-78da5de80000</link><description>哈佛大学教授。埃里克·马斯金 (Eric Maskin) 签署了一封支持总统克劳丁·盖伊 (Claudine Gay) 的信，因为她没有表示呼吁对犹太人进行种族灭绝违反了大学规定。他告诉《国土报》，“她的反应很天真”，并谈到了他认为需要做出的改变</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 08:29:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jewish-nobel-prize-laureate-explains-his-support-for-harvard-head/0000018c-7888-d7be-a1cd-78da5de80000</guid></item><item><title>四名以色列士兵在加沙南部丧生；上周受伤的士兵死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-south-gaza-soldier-wounded-last-week-dies/0000018c-7bd8-de44-a9be-7fdc5a9e0000</link><description>中士。利亚夫·阿卢什少校，军士长。 （研究）Etan Naeh，军士长。 （研究）塔尔·菲利巴和中士。一等（预备）利多·约瑟夫·卡拉瓦尼（Lidor Yosef Karavani）在加沙地带南部的战斗中阵亡，而中士。乌里贾·拜尔 (Urija Bayer) 少校因上周受伤不治身亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 08:23:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-south-gaza-soldier-wounded-last-week-dies/0000018c-7bd8-de44-a9be-7fdc5a9e0000</guid></item><item><title>新研究称圣经国王耶罗波安的“假”印章是真实的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-12-18/ty-article/fake-seal-impression-of-biblical-king-jeroboam-is-authentic-new-study-says/0000018c-7853-d98c-abef-fed7f4370000</link><description>一名核科学家在跳蚤市场购买了可疑的海豹印模。研究发现，这是真实的：一位官员对古代以色列国王耶罗波安二世的咆哮狮子印章进行了更小、更粗糙的复制品</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 08:16:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-12-18/ty-article/fake-seal-impression-of-biblical-king-jeroboam-is-authentic-new-study-says/0000018c-7853-d98c-abef-fed7f4370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正在寻找加速人质谈判的方法；消息人士称交易还有几周时间</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-eyeing-creative-ways-to-speed-up-hostage-talks-sources-say-deal-weeks-off/0000018c-7990-de5d-a9ce-7fde55020000</link><description>消息人士称，“以色列和哈马斯都无法重启谈判”。尽管摩萨德首席会见卡塔尔领导人，但本轮会谈将比第一轮更加“漫长、复杂”</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 07:05:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-eyeing-creative-ways-to-speed-up-hostage-talks-sources-say-deal-weeks-off/0000018c-7990-de5d-a9ce-7fde55020000</guid></item><item><title>随着战争目标的离去，以色列将深化和扩大加沙攻势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-set-to-deepen-and-expand-gaza-offensive-as-war-goals-slip-away/0000018c-7975-d55c-a7cc-fb77aec40000</link><description>公众对以色列战争支持的共识开始减弱，因为支持以色列战争的两个条件逐渐消失：战争的明确目的和对胜利是可以实现的理解</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 06:17:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-set-to-deepen-and-expand-gaza-offensive-as-war-goals-slip-away/0000018c-7975-d55c-a7cc-fb77aec40000</guid></item><item><title>YEARENDER——2024 年民主将走向何方？特朗普可能拥有最终决定权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/year-end/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/yearender-where-is-democracy-headed-in-2024-trump-may-have-the-final-word/0000018c-7b84-de44-a9be-7f9413b60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 06:01:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/year-end/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/yearender-where-is-democracy-headed-in-2024-trump-may-have-the-final-word/0000018c-7b84-de44-a9be-7f9413b60000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德和中央情报局负责人会见卡塔尔总理，讨论潜在的人质交易；五名以色列国防军士兵在加沙丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article-live/israeli-strike-in-damascus-kills-two-syria-reports/0000018c-7ad6-de44-a9be-7fd689f10000</link><description>以色列国防军称预备役士兵在加沙地带北部的战斗中丧生 ■ 以色列妇女在约旦河西岸疑似枪击事件中受伤 ■ 亲以色列黑客声称对导致伊朗 70% 的加油站无法使用负责 ■ 加沙还有另外两条哈马斯隧道 ■ 至少自10月7日以来，以色列有1,200名平民和士兵被杀；加沙至少 130 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 18,608 人死亡，50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 03:57:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article-live/israeli-strike-in-damascus-kills-two-syria-reports/0000018c-7ad6-de44-a9be-7fd689f10000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质告诉《60分钟》节目，哈马斯“像炫耀战利品一样向我炫耀”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/they-could-not-help-themselves-showing-me-off-as-a-trophy-freed-israeli-hostage-says/0000018c-7a73-d55c-a7cc-fb77b77e0000</link><description>亚登·罗曼-加特 (Yarden Roman-Gat) 是一位从哈马斯囚禁中获释的 36 岁母亲，她向美国节目讲述了她试图帮助其他人回家的经历，其中包括她的嫂子卡梅尔 (Carmel)。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 01:52:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-18/ty-article/.premium/they-could-not-help-themselves-showing-me-off-as-a-trophy-freed-israeli-hostage-says/0000018c-7a73-d55c-a7cc-fb77b77e0000</guid></item><item><title>我想相信以色列国防军不会射杀举着白旗的手无寸铁的平民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-17/ty-article/.highlight/i-want-to-believe-the-idf-wont-shoot-unarmed-civilians-holding-a-white-flag/0000018c-7896-d301-a3ac-fed78b050000</link><description>我不知道有多少人相信哈勒维所说的以色列国防军不会射杀投降者。落在加沙的炸弹还导致数千名乞讨者丧生。白旗并不能阻止他们</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 21:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-17/ty-article/.highlight/i-want-to-believe-the-idf-wont-shoot-unarmed-civilians-holding-a-white-flag/0000018c-7896-d301-a3ac-fed78b050000</guid></item><item><title>六名巴勒斯坦囚犯死亡后，以色列最高法院法官将视察监狱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-supreme-court-justices-to-visit-prisons-following-deaths-of-6-palestinian-inmates/0000018c-78bb-d98c-abef-febff9290000</link><description>最近几周，关于暴力和忽视以及以色列监狱中巴勒斯坦囚犯生活条件普遍恶化的证词不断增多，导致以色列决定恢复司法探视。然而，其中一些变化是战争开始后制定的官方政策的结果，最高法院签署了该政策</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 19:11:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-supreme-court-justices-to-visit-prisons-following-deaths-of-6-palestinian-inmates/0000018c-78bb-d98c-abef-febff9290000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨致人质家属：杀害哈马斯头目辛瓦尔“根本不是重点”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/gantz-to-hostages-families-killing-hamas-chief-sinwar-not-the-point-at-all/0000018c-7874-d7be-a1cd-78fef53c0000</link><description>被哈马斯扣押的以色列人质的家属在对战时内阁部长本尼·甘茨和约阿夫·加兰特发表讲话时，要求以色列国防军停止营救行动，并呼吁政府推动一项新协议，尽快释放剩余的俘虏。可能的</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 17:19:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/gantz-to-hostages-families-killing-hamas-chief-sinwar-not-the-point-at-all/0000018c-7874-d7be-a1cd-78fef53c0000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装加大对红海航运的攻击力度，美国警告将采取军事行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-warns-of-military-action-as-houthis-ramp-up-attacks-on-red-sea-shipping/0000018c-786b-d301-a3ac-feebbdac0000</link><description>考虑到伊朗干预的风险，拜登政府并不急于使用军事力量，而五角大楼表示，军方“将毫不犹豫地在我们认为必要和适当的情况下采取行动”</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 16:37:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-warns-of-military-action-as-houthis-ramp-up-attacks-on-red-sea-shipping/0000018c-786b-d301-a3ac-feebbdac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯社区的谋杀率自战争开始以来下降后大幅上升</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/murder-rate-in-israels-arab-communities-surges-after-plunging-since-start-of-war/0000018c-7853-d55c-a7cc-fb5793470000</link><description>哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列后，阿拉伯社区的凶杀率与战前六个月相比减少了一半，但现在已恢复到之前的水平。警方将这一上升归因于该国大部分地区恢复了相对正常的生活状态，以及现场警力的减少</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 15:53:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/murder-rate-in-israels-arab-communities-surges-after-plunging-since-start-of-war/0000018c-7853-d55c-a7cc-fb5793470000</guid></item><item><title>第三季度 GDP 下调、通胀放缓后以色列可能降息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israel-rate-cuts-possible-after-q3-gdp-revised-down-inflation-eases/0000018c-7832-d301-a3ac-fef3d4460000</link><description>2023年以色列经济增长放缓，部分原因是战争的负面影响。明年的增长很大程度上取决于战争的持续时间以及冲突是否仍然局限于加沙或蔓延到其他战线</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 15:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/israel-rate-cuts-possible-after-q3-gdp-revised-down-inflation-eases/0000018c-7832-d301-a3ac-fef3d4460000</guid></item></channel></rss>